## Overview

This guide documents the security updates made to **liri-node-app** to address multiple critical vulnerabilities from deprecated and outdated packages. All deprecated packages have been replaced with secure, actively maintained alternatives.

**Update Date:** 2026-04-10  
**Status:** Recommended for immediate implementation

