## Installation Instructions

### 1. Clean Install (Recommended)

```bash
# Remove old dependencies
rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json

# Install new dependencies
npm install

# Verify installation
npm ls
```

### 2. Update Current Installation

```bash
# Update all packages
npm update

# Install new packages
npm install spotify-web-api-node date-fns cli-table3

# Remove deprecated packages
npm uninstall node-spotify-api moment request request-promise
```

### 3. Verify Package Versions

```bash
npm list --depth=0
```

Expected output:
```
liri-node-app@1.0.0
├── axios@1.6.x
├── cli-table3@0.6.x
├── date-fns@2.30.x
├── dotenv@16.3.x
├── spotify-web-api-node@5.0.x
